She looked at Stringtra as she walked out.  She wakled back over to 
Quickstrick, "Commander, is it safe for her to leave while being in her 
condition, with her arm like that? You might want to go and talk to her 
commander.  She looks like she need a friend."
She looked down, "I may be out of line commander and mey be up for disapline 
as a result of my taking to you like this, but I think it would be best if 
you talk to her."  She turned and walked back to Scorponok.
